rows.label: qst202603_msg0001
rows.name: I have been waiting for you.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0002
rows.name:
The Queen herself came all
this way to greet us...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0003
rows.name: I feel like a guest of honor, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0004
rows.name:
We are honored by your
personal welcome...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0005
rows.name: Please raise your head, Meleph-dono.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0006
rows.name:
I must apologize for receiving
you in such a place.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0007
rows.name: The situation is urgent...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Could you please inform
us of the situation?

rows.label: qst202603_msg0009
rows.name: Understood.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0010
rows.name:
Currently, two Herridot Laias have been
confirmed in Invidia, and they have already
repelled our subjugation teams three times...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0012
rows.name: Two of them?!

rows.label: qst202603_msg0013
rows.name:
Yes. With the small number of Drivers
in our army, we were no match...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0014
rows.name:
We also requested help from the Merc
Group, but they struggled against the
unknown monster and were defeated.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0015
rows.name:
It is difficult for our
forces to subjugate them.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0024
rows.name:
That is why I requested the cooperation
of you, who have the Holy Grail and
other excellent Blades.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0016
rows.name:
All right, let's go
defeat them right away.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0017
rows.name: I am grateful to you...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0018
rows.name:
The Herridot Laias are currently
deep within the Gullet Pass.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0019
rows.name: Understood.

rows.label: qst202603_msg0020
rows.name: Ten'i...[ML:Dash ] can you do it?

rows.label: qst202603_msg0021
rows.name: Of course...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202603_msg0022
rows.name:
Let us subjugate them as
quickly as possible...[ML:Dash ]
